snippet.title: How to Play SLIMECORE
snippet.description:
SLIMECORE is a squad-based strategic hero brawler featuring a dynamic roguelite augment system. Take down the competition using a blend of sharp mechanical skill and strategic game knowledge.

Signup details at https://discord.gg/SLIMECORE. Play Oct 21-26!
